{"tid":380760,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有腸發炎經驗既師兄入一入黎幫幫手","createTime":"2017-08-30T11:19:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T13:13:08.000Z","uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"60b3545790fba409292f0c5ee8101cabd3c72586","tid":380760,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:19:29.000Z","msg":"我２０歲<br />\n肚痾左成年，每日至少３次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出門口一次，出到去起碼２次，返屋企又１次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔可以去Ｄ附近冇廁所既地方，唔係就會賴出黎（講真）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁怕冷氣，一入地鐵商場超市一定要著褸，如果唔係又肚痛<br />\n最近照左腸鏡，有瘜肉切左，同埋發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痾Ｄ屎會有白色粘液痴住<br />\n有冇師兄有相關經驗，或者有方法醫治<br />\n因為醫院果邊仲未覆診，但我好驚<br />\n好驚係果Ｄ咩潰瘍性結腸炎，冇得斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n請救救我，生不如死，玩都冇力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2698bfe5106467cffd5816a833930f2033159ab","tid":380760,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:11:13.000Z","msg":"係咪冇人幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7be63936861a6639a1734804c51f87f58a66da14","tid":380760,"uid":139830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T13:12:36.000Z","msg":"痾左成年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"